Revision history for Plack-Middleware-Recorder

0.06 November 02 2016
     - Include META.json (Thanks, Sean Zellmer!)

0.05 April 12 2015
     - Fix a test to run better on CPAN testers (Thanks, Slaven ReziÄ‡!)

0.04 April 08 2015
     - POD/prereqs fixes (thanks, Anthony Brummett!)
